{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>#The following gameplay content is included in the demo version.</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Background</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Evil spreads, and demons run rampant. Manage the Pagoda, and shelter the people.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Simulation</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Before the invasion, gather resources and strengthen your power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430870/extras/Tutorial_Censer.gif?t=1736934574\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fulfill pilgrims' prayers to earn offerings of copper coins and materials.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430870/extras/Tutorial_Library.gif?t=1736934574\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0Upgrade formation scrolls to boost combat attributes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demon Invasion</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430870/extras/Tutorial_DivinePower.gif?t=1736934574\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430870/extras/Tutorial_GetMana.gif?t=1736934574\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Deploy, Reach, and Collect.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose Divine Power, deploy Talismans, and collect Mana upon reaching again to level up your power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3430870/extras/Tutorial_InvadeAndDamage.gif?t=1736934574\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dice Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Roll dice to compete with Talisman points. The outcome is uncertain\u2014victory or d